title: Letter to Kafei
text: [{"text":"\"You were given a letter to Kafei! Quick! Deliver it for her! Take it to a mailbox.\""}]

title: Note to Mom
text: [{"text":"For the item from Majora's Mask, see Letter to Mama."},{"text":"\"You accepted a Note to Mom! It's so sad you could almost cry.\""}]

title: Father's Letter
text: [{"text":"\"You accepted Father's Letter! It is a letter from a father addressed to his son.\""}]

title: Auru's Memo
text: [{"text":"\"You got Auru's memo! Auru wrote this to Fyer of Lake Hylia.\""}]

title: Letter in a Bottle
text: [{"text":"'This article is about the Ocarina of Time item. For the A Link Between Worlds item, see Message in a Bottle."},{"text":"\"Are you saying my father asked you to come here to save me? I'd never ask anyone to do such a thing! \"Letter in a Bottle?\" I have no idea what you're talking about! My father is worried about me? I don't care!\""},{"text":"\"Help me. I'm waiting for you inside Lord Jabu-Jabu's belly.\""}]

title: Jolene's Letter
text: [{"text":"\"Jolene wrote this letter to her younger sister. She might be happy if you delivered it to her.\""}]

title: Cawlin's Letter
text: [{"text":"\"Greetings. My love for you is wider than the horizon and deeper than the clouds. I would very much like it if you would go out with me.\nYour brave knight,\nCawlin\""}]

title: Renado's Letter
text: [{"text":"\"You got Renado's letter! It carefully details how to treat Ilia to get her memory back.\""}]

title: Letter to Mama
text: [{"text":"For the item from The Wind Waker, see Note to Mom."},{"text":"\"Now Kafei... He says he wants you to take this to his mother.\""}]

title: Stationery
text: [{"text":"\"You got Stationery! Who will you write to?\""}]

title: Zelda's Letter
text: [{"text":"\"This is Link... He is under my orders to save Hyrule.\""}]

title: Ooccoo's Note
text: [{"text":"\"Ooccoo has things to do. So she will remain here. If you return, let's get together.\""}]

title: Finley's Letter
text: [{"text":"This article is a stub. You can help Zeldapedia by  expanding it."}]

title: Letter (Four Swords Adventures)
text: [{"text":"\"You got the Letter! Savior of romance!\""}]

title: Letter of Introduction
text: [{"text":"\"OK. Take this Letter of Introduction to the Graceful Goron! If you show that to the Graceful Goron, he'll understand.\""}]
